solution=fixed&amp;milestone=5.2.1&amp;order=priority\">lista completa de alteraÃ§Ãµes no Trac</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>O WordPress 5.2.1 foi uma versÃ£o de manutenÃ§Ã£o com ciclo de lanÃ§amento curto. Espera-se que a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?milestone=5.2.2\">versÃ£o 5.2.2</a>&nbsp;tambÃ©m siga um ritmo de aproximadamente duas semanas.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>VocÃª pode&nbsp;<a href=\"https://br.wordpress.org/download/\">baixar o WordPress 5.2.1</a>&nbsp;ou ir em&nbsp;<strong>Painel â AtualizaÃ§Ãµes</strong>&nbsp;e clicar em&nbsp;<strong>Atualizar agora</strong>. Sites com suporte a atualizaÃ§Ãµes automÃ¡ticas em segundo plano jÃ¡ comeÃ§aram a se atualizar.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>O WordPress 5.2.1 foi coliderado por&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/desrosj/\">Jonathan Desrosiers</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/earnjam/\">William Earnhardt</a>&nbsp;e traz colaboraÃ§Ãµes de outras 52 pessoas. Agradecemos a todos os que tornaram este lanÃ§amento possÃ­vel!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/xavortm/\">Alex Dimitrov</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tellyworth/\">Alex Shiels</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/afercia/\">Andrea Fercia</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aduth/\">Andrew Duthie</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/azaozz/\">Andrew Ozz</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rarst/\">Andrey âRarstâ Savchenko</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/afragen/\">Andy Fragen</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anischarolia/\">anischarolia</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/birgire/\">Birgir Erlendsson (birgire)</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/chesio/\">chesio</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/chetan200891/\">Chetan Prajapati</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/daxelrod/\">daxelrod</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dkarfa/\">Debabrata Karfa</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/odminstudios/\">Dima</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dd32/\">Dion Hulse</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ocean90/\">Dominik Schilling</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/iseulde/\">Ella van Durpe</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/edocev/\">Emil Dotsev</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sachyya-sachet/\">ghoul</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gziolo/\">Grzegorz (Greg) ZiÃ³Åkowski</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gwwar/\">gwwar</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hareesh-pillai/\">Hareesh</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ianbelanger/\">Ian Belanger</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/imath/\">imath</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/audrasjb/\">Jb Audras</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jeremyfelt/\">Jeremy Felt</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joen/\">Joen Asmussen</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/desrosj/\">Jonathan Desrosiers</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/spacedmonkey/\">Jonny Harris</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/chanthaboune/\">Josepha</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jrf/\">jrf</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kjellr/\">kjellr</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/clorith/\">Marius L. J.</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mikengarrett/\">MikeNGarrett</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dimadin/\">Milan DiniÄ</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mukesh27/\">Mukesh Panchal</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/onlanka/\">onlanka</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/paragoninitiativeenterprises/\">paragoninitiativeenterprises</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/parkcityj/\">parkcityj</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/peterwilsoncc/\">Peter Wilson</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/presskopp/\">Presskopp</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/youknowriad/\">Riad Benguella</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sergeybiryukov/\">Sergey Biryukov</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/netweb/\">Stephen Edgar</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sebastienserre/\">SÃ©bastien SERRE</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tfrommen/\">Thorsten Frommen</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hedgefield/\">Tim Hengeveld</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/timothyblynjacobs/\">Timothy Jacobs</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/timph/\">timph</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tobiasbg/\">TobiasBg</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tonybogdanov/\">tonybogdanov</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tobifjellner/\">Tor-Bjorn Fjellner</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/earnjam/\">William Earnhardt</a> e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/fierevere/\">Yui</a>.<br></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n				\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n										\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"WordPress Translation Day 4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://br.wordpress.org/2019/05/09/wordpress-translation-day-4/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"