 class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://br.wordpress.org/files/2019/05/wptd4-header-1024x533.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1518\" srcset=\"https://br.wordpress.org/files/2019/05/wptd4-header-1024x533.jpg 1024w, https://br.wordpress.org/files/2019/05/wptd4-header-300x156.jpg 300w, https://br.wordpress.org/files/2019/05/wptd4-header-768x400.jpg 768w, https://br.wordpress.org/files/2019/05/wptd4-header.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<span id=\"more-1516\"></span>\n\n\n\n<p>Nesta quarta ediÃ§Ã£o do evento, o Brasil nÃ£o vai ficar de fora. Confira abaixo os meetups organizados pela nossa comunidade:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>SÃ£o Paulo</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>HorÃ¡rio: 14h Ã s 18h<br>Local: FCamara &#8211; Rua Bela Cintra, 986<br>Link: <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/pt-BR/wpsampa/events/260963644/\">https://www.meetup.com/pt-BR/wpsampa/events/260963644/</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>BalneÃ¡rio CamboriÃº</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>HorÃ¡rio: 10h Ã s 12h<br>Local: Stor7 &#8211; Rua 906, 711<br>Link: <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/pt-BR/Meetup-de-WordPress-Balneario-Camboriu/events/261024142/\">https://www.meetup.com/pt-BR/Meetup-de-WordPress-Balneario-Camboriu/events/261024142/</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Blumenau</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>HorÃ¡rio: 10h Ã s 12h<br>Local:  Universidade Regional de Blumenau &#8211; Rua AntÃ´nio da Veiga, 140, Victor Konder<br>Link: <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/pt-BR/Blumenau-WordPress-Meetup/events/261015137/\">https://www.meetup.com/pt-BR/Blumenau-WordPress-Meetup/events/261015137/</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Curitiba</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>HorÃ¡rio: 9h Ã s 11h30min<br>Local: Jupter &#8211; Rua Gen. Carneiro, 1031 Â· Curitiba<br>Link: <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/pt-BR/wpcuritiba/events/260729102/\">https://www.meetup.com/pt-BR/wpcuritiba/events/260729102/</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Esta Ã© uma Ã³tima oportunidade para conhecer melhor a comunidade WordPress no Brasil, compartilhar dicas e informaÃ§Ãµes, alÃ©m de ajudar a traduzir plugins, temas e outros projetos do WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>NÃ£o fique de fora. Inscreva-se do meetup da sua cidade ou participe online do evento atravÃ©s do <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/polyglots/handbook/about/teams/local-slacks/#south-america\">Slack da comunidade brasileira de WordPress</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" />\n\n\n\n<p>Agradecimento especial para o <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/samrgomes/\">@samrgomes</a> pela ajuda com a criaÃ§Ã£o do post.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:35:\"https://br.wordpress.org/news/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"\n	hourly	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"\n	1	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:8:{s:6:\"server\";s:5:\"nginx\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Wed, 09 Oct 2019 14:36:53 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:34:\"application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8\";s:6:\"x-olaf\";s:3:\"â\";s:13:\"last-modified\";s:29:\"Wed, 06 Sep 2017 19:17:40 GMT\";s:4:\"link\";s:61:\"<https://br.wordpress.org/wp-json/>; rel=\"https://api.w.org/\"\";s:15:\"x-frame-options\";s:10:\"SAMEORIGIN\";s:4:\"x-nc\";s:9:\"HIT ord 1\";}}s:5:\"build\";s:14:\"20130911040210\";}', 'no');
